Title: The new Microsoft Edge for Windows 10 Version 1809 for x64-based Systems (KB4584642)
Description: Install this update to upgrade devices from Microsoft Edge legacy to the new Microsoft Edge, which is based on the Chromium open source engine. For more details about the new Microsoft Edge, please see the associated Microsoft Knowledge Base (KB) article. After you install this update, the changes will not take effect until a reboot occurs.
